snippet.title: Mooloolaba Yacht Club is sailing into next 50 years
snippet.content: THE Mooloolaba Yacht Club celebrated its 50th anniversary and launch of its commemorative book on July 22 at See Restaurant at The Wharf Mooloolaba. More than 70 members and friends enjoyed a lively evening of storytelling and sharing memories from the club's past days.
